ebook description:
Ebook is a MEAN stack social network websie. Created learning Node and Typescript 2 weeks :)). Currently the project is running on local.
With some main features: CURD api, authentication with jwt
niwfy description:
A comic website made with Angular in 2 month. Data crawled from nettruyen.com and storage on Firebase .
 Include features such as: searching, authentication with Firebase, read comic, rating, comment/reply.
rem description:
Rem is my wif..., I said some fool. Rem is a movie website made by Vue3. Using api from ophim.com.
